Craig Thomas
Vice President, Manufacturing & Operations
Craig Thomas joined Ergotron/CFT in 2004 as Director of China Operations. In 2005, he was promoted to Vice President China Operations and General Manager. Craig is responsible for Ergotron’s China Factory with primary emphasis on New Products Introduction, Manufacturing, Quality, MRP, Procurement, Warehousing and Distribution of Ergotron products. He brings more than 30 years Manufacturing Operations experience to our Global Manufacturing Operations Team. Since joining Ergotron, he has succeeded in establishing a World Class Factory Operation with best in class product quality and product cost.
Craig has gained significant Senior Management experience in International arenas of Manufacturing Operations while serving as VP/GM of factories in Malaysia and Philippines. Early in his career he gained high volume manufacturing experience in Japan, Korea and Singapore serving as VP/Director of New Products Introduction in the HDD Storage industry.
Craig is very passionate about training employees in different countries to become skilled Operations managers. He believes it is good for the employees and good for the company.
In his free time, Craig enjoys traveling in Asia and playing golf with his son, Jason.






 






















