lity to create protocols regarding bed bugs. Let Craig Thomas Pest Control be your partner in preventing or solving your bed bug infestations in your home, housing complex, hotel or other type of facility.FleasCockroachesSilverfishBeesSpring. In the spring we provide our first exterior treatment to the home to aid against crawling insects like ants and flying insects like bees. This also includes minimum exclusion to cracks and crevices which are entry points of insects and rodents. In addition, your interior inspection and service will be provided as well.WaspsTicksEarwigsMosquitoesFliesFall. Establishing another exterior barrier on the exterior of your home will help prevent fall insects like cluster flies. This helps prevent pest problems during the winter months and into the following spring. Minor exclusion to cracks, crevices and gaps will be sealed to prevent rodents from making entry into the home during the colder months.  In addition, your interior inspection will be performed with monitoring rodent equipment (if applicable) and any other treatment if needed.CentipedesMillipedesMothsStinging InsectsAs a homeowner, it’s up to you to decide what’s best for your home and family. No matter where you live in the Hudson Valley you can count on the team at Craig Thomas Pest Control, in partnership with Orkin Pest Control, to help protect your health, home and property from insects and rodents. Our ongoing pest management programs are designed to eliminate pest and maintain a pest free environment. Offering a wide variety of programs, each designed with your home, your family and the environment in mind. We offer homeowners one treatment options or maintenance programs, however many insects and rodent are difficult to control in just one visit. Our residential pest control services are prescribed to your specific needs targeting everything from ants, mice, stinging insects and even proactive termite detection – protecting your investment is an easy decision.Bird C