          Green Solutions        

Imagine an environment with reduced pests and pesticides. 
Craig Thomas Pest Control, in partnership with Orkin Pest Control, proudly offers the Hudson Valley an organic solution to their pest management problems.  EcoSmart technologies contain a unique ingredient, octopamine which targets insect’s exoskeleton. Mammals, birds, fish do not have receptors for octopamine, therefore are not affected and remain completely safe.  Research proves EcoSmarts botanical products are just as effective as conventional products in the ability to kill insects and provide control. Whether you require treatment indoor or outdoor, these products made with essential oils, fragrant by nature are guaranteed to solve your problem. 

Proven Effective
Safe around Children
Safe around Pets
Safe for birds and wildlife
Safe for groundwater sources
Safe allowed on label by FDA
100% FDA safe ingredients 

Why consider a green alternative?

Someone in your family suffers from allergies or asthma.
There are children, pets, pregnant women or elderly. 
You want to use the most natural options in and around your home

Using nature’s ingredients, Craig Thomas Pest Control can provide you with the security knowing the materials used in and around your property are derived from the environment.  Choosing an effective pest management company in the Hudson Valley is an easy decision when you choose Craig Thomas Pest Control, just like choosing an effective, low risk option to rid your insect problems. We service Hyde Park, Hopewell, Pawling, Kingston, New Paltz, Woodstock, Goshen and Warwick. For a full list of contact numbers and service areas, click here.

 





