Craig Thomas Pest Control, in partnership with Orkin Pest Control, understands all customers’ needs are unique and all need their own solution. This is why Craig Thomas Pest Control is flexible, meeting the demands of every customer and exceeding their expectations, while protecting the health and property of the customer and the environment.
Pest management covers all types of places, from residential to commercial and from industrial to institutional because in the end, the goals are the same. Everyone wants to live and work in a healthy environment free from pests and pest damage. At Craig Thomas Pest Control, we make sure you can get on with the business of living and working without this worry. Call us and we’ll make sure all of your pest management needs are met, efficiently and with a smile.










